name: Schedule 15N-Machine Learning-Open Source and Digitization - Demystified

messages.textToSpeech: How else may I help you?

messages.speech: Have you ever wondered how to build a mobile application or use Machine Learning? This is aHands-On workshop where you will build a mobile Android application, learn and applyMachine Learning and automate the code through open source automation framework -Karate.How Do I Benefit?You will gain experience in using Android Studio to build mobile application; You will learn how to use TensorFlow for Machine Learning.
